Windows client prior to 14.50. Attackers with local control of the 
Windows client can use it to trigger a denial of service.",2026-04-30T21:16:32.883,0.0,UNKNOWN,UNKNOWN,UNKNOWN,CWE-121,CWE-121,,False,0.0
CVE-2026-40950,"CVE-2026-40950 is a buffer overflow vulnerability in the Secure Access 
